en: Eegimaa is mainly spoken in Mof-Ávvi , a former kingdom of 10 villages located to the west of Ziguinchor , the capital city of the former administrative region of Casamance in the south of Senegal .
baseline: Eegimaa主要在Mof-Ávvi,一个位于西南部塞内加尔前行政区卡萨曼斯的首都Ziguinchor的10个村庄的前王国。
zh: 阿瓦维(Mof-Ávvi)是一个位于塞内加尔南部前行政区卡萨曼斯的首都西吉宁科尔(Ziguinchor)的10个村庄的旧王国。

en: Enjambment takes place when a syntactic unit is broken up across two lines of poetry  , giving rise to different stylistic effects  , or creating double interpretations for the enjambed lines  .
baseline: 插曲发生在一个语法单元在诗歌两行之间被分割时,产生不同的风格效果,或为插曲线创造双重解释。
